Ayo.  Ayo pergi.

00:01:07.120 --> 00:01:08.840
Mudah!  Berikan aku tanganmu.

00:01:11.800 --> 00:01:13.520
Apa yang telah terjadi?

00:01:14.840 --> 00:01:16.720
Kemana perginya Mohan dan Radha?

00:01:52.440 --> 00:01:54.240
Mohan, katakan sesuatu.  Mohan!

00:01:54.320 --> 00:01:55.160
Mohan!  -Mohan!

00:01:55.240 --> 00:01:56.840
Mohan!  -Mohan!

00:02:18.840 --> 00:02:20.000
Sedikit lagi waktu.

00:02:20.400 --> 00:02:22.240
Kita telah sampai sejauh ini.

00:02:24.840 --> 00:02:25.840
Apakah kamu baik-baik saja?

00:02:26.320 --> 00:02:27.480
Ayo pergi.

00:02:50.920 --> 00:02:52.040
Mohan!

00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:53.360
Mohan!

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:56.440
Mohan!  -Mohan!

00:02:56.600 --> 00:02:57.680
Mohan!

00:02:57.880 --> 00:03:00.400
Mohan!  Katakan sesuatu, Mohan!

00:03:00.480 --> 00:03:01.520
Mohan!  -Mohan!

00:03:10.800 --> 00:03:12.200
Mohan!

00:03:17.880 --> 00:03:19.680
Oke.  Pasang ini ke katrol.

00:03:20.080 --> 00:03:21.120
Bergegaslah.

00:03:23.040 --> 00:03:25.280
Mohan!  Mohan, hati-hati!

00:03:26.960 --> 00:03:28.880
Radha.  Berikan aku tanganmu.

00:03:56.720 --> 00:03:57.920
Mudah.

00:03:58.400 --> 00:04:00.080
